た。富野博士は誘拐した少女達の生命を生贄に、四方天照を生き返らせようとする。儀式は魔実也の仕掛けた爆薬によって止められたが、それをきっかけに研究成果を狙った世界各国の軍隊が入り乱れる戦いとなる。ついに血迷ったドイツ軍将校がピラミッドを爆破。魔実也らは辛くも脱出したが、夢破れた富野博士は恩人四方天照の死体と運命を共にし、事件は闇に葬られた。","name":"夢幻紳士 冒険活劇編","name_cn":"梦幻绅士 冒险活剧编","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"辻初樹","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1987","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"橋本以蔵","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"戸田恵子","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ぎゃろっぷ","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1987年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"看完就删","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"八奈見乗児","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立ova","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"赛璐珞","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"滝口順平","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"梦幻绅士 冒险活剧编"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Mugen Shinshi: Bouken Katsugeki Hen"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"发售日","value":"1987年02月21日"},{"key":"演出助理","value":"演出助手：高本宣弘"},{"key":"音楽","value":"野人 (NOHITO)"},{"key":"作画监督助理","value":"作画监督補佐：佐藤雄三"},{"key":"制作","value":"ビクター音楽産業株式会社"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":22,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":2,"4":4,"5":8,"6":6,"7":1,"8":1,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.1},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":3,"dropped":6,"wish":15,"collect":34,"doing":2},"id":83751,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["OVA"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1987-02-07","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/b8/af/20266_rtw8c.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/b8/af/20266_rtw8c.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/b8/af/20266_rtw8c.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/b8/af/20266_rtw8c.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/b8/af/20266_rtw8c.jpg"},"summary":"在公元(西历)2087年，地球和宇宙正被战火包围着，提倡了人类再生的“基格诺斯帝国”，在月球成立了军事独裁政权向地球联邦发动了征服世界的战争。\r\n在宇宙殖民地亚路卡亚居住的三个少年:健`赖度`达布，偶然得到了地球联邦军从基格诺斯中，盗取秘密开发的机甲战士(Metal Armor)“威龙”起动用磁盘而登录成为其驾驶员。\r\n因为盗取威龙引起了基格诺斯使用熔岩炮破坏殖民卫星，三人便开始和基格诺斯抗争到底，并在旅途中遇上了开发机甲战士的布拉顿博士，他的子女马勒(基格诺斯苍鹰)和莉达(女主角)，会否令整个宇宙和地球局势扭转?","name":"機甲戦記ドラグナー","name_cn":"机甲战记威龙","tags":[{"name":"SUNRISE","count":50,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1987","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神田武幸","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"高桥良辅","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"龙骑小队","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大河原邦男","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧番","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"菊池正美","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Dragonar","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1987年2月","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"サンライズ","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战登场作","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"高橋良輔","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"鈴木良武","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大塚芳忠","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大貫健一","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"五武冬史","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"渡辺俊幸","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"龙骑3基友","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"robo","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补旧番","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"机甲战记威龙"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Metal Armor Dragonar"},{"v":"机甲战记龙骑"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"48"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1987年2月7日"},{"key":"放送星期","value":"星期六"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.dragonar.net/"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"名古屋テレビ"},{"key":"其他电视台","value":